# AI/LLM-specific names/directories (case-insensitive blocks)
*[Oo]pen[Aa]i*
*[Gg]emini*
*[Aa]nthropic*
*[Cc]laude*
*[Hh]ugging[Ff]ace*
*[Hh]uggingface*
*[Ll][Ll][Mm]*
